  "Description": "The CFT deploys McAfee Network Security Platform AWS Solution. It creates a VPC, Public(Management) subnet, Internet Gateway, Public Route Table, IAM roles, Security Groups, Network security Manager, Controller and Network Security Platform Sensor with single interface (with an autoscaling option)",
